---
title: Double Teriyaki Beef & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Ginger Rice
description: It doesn’t get much more simple and delicious than this beef and broccoli stir-fry. Our teriyaki sauce is the perfect
addition, bringing tons of flavour in just one ingredient. And don’t forget the fragrant rice - the subtle heat of our punchy ginger paste adds an aromatic twist. No need to wait, dig in while it’s hot!
